irk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqNpocWcFirk&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNpnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=16f1cbc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qNpocWcFirk</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>大家仲記唔記得曾經答應左咩?</strong></span><br />\n<blockquote><strong>兄弟爬山 各有各做 齊上齊落 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不受傷 不被捕 不分化 不篤灰 不割蓆 不譴責 不撤不散 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n互相提點 互相協助 互補不足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>大家仲記唔記得當初叫過既口號?</strong></span><br />\n<blockquote><strong>五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n獨立調查 撤回惡法 平反暴動 撤銷檢控 雙真普選<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\nStand with Hong Kong! Fight for Freedom!<br />\nLiberate Hong Kong! Revolution of our time!</strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">香港人 加油</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港人 反抗</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人 報仇</span></span></strong></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>大家仲記唔記得自己係點進化?</strong></span><br />\n<blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">香港人 加油</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港人 反抗</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人 報仇</span></span></strong></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>大家仲記唔記得我地既信念?</strong></span><br />\n<strong><blockquote>無大台抗爭, 流水式抗爭<br />\n寧化飛灰 不作浮塵<br />\n勇武抗爭, 以武制暴<br />\n相信前線所做的一切<br />\nBe Water!<br />\nIdeas are bulletproof.<br />\n5 Demands, Not one less!<br />\nLiberate Hong Kong! Revolution of our time!<br />\nWe shall never surrender!<br />\nNo one left behind!</blockquote></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>各位手足, </strong><br />\n打漏左既話，幫我補充一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打錯左既話，幫我修改一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地唔好再犯5年前既錯，緊記好不容易先行到依步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行左咁耐又點可能一次都無錯過，錯左既我地要檢討，諗下點改善，緊記失敗教訓，未來做得更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">願榮光歸香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位好好保護自己，奮戰落去，相約他朝煲底再相見，好嗎? </span></span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:46:21.000Z","msg":"各位手足，關於送林奠去大灣區的partition，尋日激增20000幾人(差不多簽署人數的10%)!，證明大家都好希望將佢舉家永遠封印晌大灣區！<br />\n<br />\n嘅然係咁就唔好停了，跟據早前民意調查有7成人唔妥佢嘅，咁我地嘅目標係咪應該set晌490萬個簽名呢？<br />\n<br />\n小弟英文唔好，如果可以的話，亦希望各手足可以幫手將佢推上國際！<br />\n<br />\n唔使俾錢架，簽完再share就唔使比錢㗎啦。<span style=\"color: red;\">最新消息：今朝22萬9千了！目標：490萬</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-home-office-uk-home-office-should-revoke-carrie-lam-s-family-citizenship?cs_tk=AtIXNHLitQ7NOzo40F0AAXicyyvNyQEABF8BvKv03Ej5HuubaSSmIizKZKU%3D&amp;utm_campaign=514ad83a9aaf489a936c80aa7705b65d&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_source=recruit_sign_digest&amp;utm_term=cs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-home-office-uk-home-office-should-revoke-carrie-lam-s-family-citizenship%3Fcs_tk%3DAtIXNHLitQ7NOzo40F0AAXicyyvNyQEABF8BvKv03Ej5HuubaSSmIizKZKU%253D%26utm_campaign%3D514ad83a9aaf489a936c80aa7705b65d%26utm_medium%3Demail%26utm_source%3Drecruit_sign_digest%26utm_term%3Dcs&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNpnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=00dae2b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-home-office-uk-home-office-should-revoke-carrie-lam-s-family-citizenship?cs_tk=AtIXNHLitQ7NOzo40F0AAXicyyvNyQEABF8BvKv03Ej5HuubaSSmIizKZKU%3D&amp;utm_campaign=514ad83a9aaf489a936c80aa7705b65d&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_source=recruit_sign_digest&amp;utm_term=cs</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hs8wPcW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHs8wPcW.jpg&h=66458b29&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"881f324bf99b1eb8444b25d4375c16cf18df4f7b","tid":1740574,"uid":217336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:47:20.000Z","msg":"又黎浪漫主義"},{"pid":"781123c2235becedfa5565731704b43b4f64fb8a","tid":1740574,"uid":1806,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8af413a8ccba6ded73f665dd4e58a4d70e9fe60d","tid":1740574,"uid":23416,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:45:50.000Z","msg":"一直覺得呢d浪漫煽情野  好嘔心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:47:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望提升返士氣"},{"pid":"013f1f8a9db41509b3c629e4c7df3c37bbff9de7","tid":1740574,"uid":302917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:48:07.000Z","msg":"個<br />\n「香港人 加油<br />\n香港人 反抗<br />\n香港人 報仇」<br />\n<br />\n睇到喊咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港人唔好退喇，我地冇退路喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77a6b5c4c6aa55286649c632d9e8727b3adc5900","tid":1740574,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:48:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6be26cdcb837a30f593780a259d45ed063031005","tid":1740574,"uid":137786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:49:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba6a3ec0b392859af28