pan style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>大家仲記唔記得曾經答應左咩?</strong></span><br />\n<blockquote><strong>兄弟爬山 各有各做 齊上齊落 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不受傷 不被捕 不分化 不篤灰 不割蓆 不譴責 不撤不散 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n互相提點 互相協助 互補不足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>大家仲記唔記得當初叫過既口號?</strong></span><br />\n<blockquote><strong>五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n獨立調查 撤回惡法 平反暴動 撤銷檢控 雙真普選<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\nStand with Hong Kong! Fight for Freedom!<br />\nLiberate Hong Kong! Revolution of our time!</strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">香港人 加油</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港人 反抗</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人 報仇</span></span></strong></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>大家仲記唔記得自己係點進化?</strong></span><br />\n<blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">香港人 加油</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港人 反抗</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人 報仇</span></span></strong></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>大家仲記唔記得我地既信念?</strong></span><br />\n<strong><blockquote>無大台抗爭, 流水式抗爭<br />\n寧化飛灰 不作浮塵<br />\n勇武抗爭, 以武制暴<br />\n相信前線所做的一切<br />\nBe Water!<br />\nIdeas are bulletproof.<br />\n5 Demands, Not one less!<br />\nLiberate Hong Kong! Revolution of our time!<br />\nWe shall never surrender!<br />\nNo one left behind!</blockquote></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>各位手足, </strong><br />\n打漏左既話，幫我補充一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打錯左既話，幫我修改一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地唔好再犯5年前既錯，緊記好不容易先行到依步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行左咁耐又點可能一次都無錯過，錯左既我地要檢討，諗下點改善，緊記失敗教訓，未來做得更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">願榮光歸香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位好好保護自己，奮戰落去，相約他朝煲底再相見，好嗎? </span></span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:51:14.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"}]}